OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776272750
OL,3,CProsecutor 'does not recall knowing
OL,4,CCalocane had students' names in
OL,5,Cweapons bag'
OL,7,FThe Nottingham attack prosecutor has
OL,8,Fsaid he does not recall knowing that
OL,9,Ftriple killer Valdo Calocane had
OL,10,Fcarried the names of three students in
OL,11,Fhis weapons bag, but the information
OL,12,Fwould not have affected his decisions
OL,13,Fon the case.
OL,15,FCalocane is detained indefinitely in a
OL,16,Fhigh-security hospital after
OL,17,Fprosecutors accepted his not guilty
OL,18,Fpleas to murder on the grounds of
OL,19,Fdiminished responsibility in January
OL,20,F2024.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776272750
OL,3,CProsecutor 'does not recall knowing
OL,4,CCalocane had students' names in
OL,5,Cweapons bag'
OL,7,FThe former University of Nottingham
OL,8,Fmechanical engineering student fatally
OL,9,Fstabbed undergraduates at the same
OL,10,Funiversity, Barnaby Webber and Grace
OL,11,FO'Malley-Kumar, both 19, on Ilkeston
OL,12,FRoad, Nottingham, in the early hours
OL,13,Fof June 13 2023.
OL,15,FHe went on to kill grandfather Ian
OL,16,FCoates, 65, in the Mapperley Park area
OL,17,Faround an hour later, stealing his van
OL,18,Fand using it to run over pedestrians
OL,19,Fat two locations in Nottingham city
OL,20,Fcentre.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776272750
OL,3,CProsecutor 'does not recall knowing
OL,4,CCalocane had students' names in
OL,5,Cweapons bag'
OL,7,FAt the Nottingham Inquiry in London,
OL,8,FKarim Khalil KC, the prosecutor in the
OL,9,Fcase, said Calocane's victims were not
OL,10,F"pre-selected".
OL,12,FHowever, Rachel Langdale KC, for the
OL,13,Finquiry, put to him on Monday that the
OL,14,Ffirst two people Calocane killed were
OL,15,Fstudents walking home from a night out
OL,16,Fin a student area, and he had the
OL,17,Fnames of three other students on a
OL,18,Fpiece of a paper in his bag.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776272750
OL,3,CProsecutor 'does not recall knowing
OL,4,CCalocane had students' names in
OL,5,Cweapons bag'
OL,7,FShe also questioned Mr Khalil on
OL,8,FCalocane allegedly assaulting and
OL,9,Ffixating on his former student
OL,10,Fflatmate.
OL,12,FMr Khalil, who prosecuted Soham
OL,13,Fmurderer Ian Huntley, said: "I was not
OL,14,Faware that he had any knowledge of
OL,15,Feither of his first two victims or
OL,16,Fthat they were, in fact, students."
OL,26,@uD@]OUxD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776272750
OL,3,CProsecutor 'does not recall knowing
OL,4,CCalocane had students' names in
OL,5,Cweapons bag'
OL,7,FCounsel responded: "Well they were in
OL,8,Fa student area, it wouldn't have been
OL,9,Fdifficult to deduce they were
OL,10,Fstudents... you've seen the footage,
OL,11,Fwould that have been difficult to
OL,12,Fassess that there were likely students
OL,13,Fwalking back from a night out?"
OL,15,FMr Khalil said: "They may have been
OL,16,Fbut his third victim plainly wasn't a
OL,17,Fstudent and nor were his fourth, fifth
OL,18,Fand sixth victims students.
OL,26,@oD@TOUuD@_O]wD@QOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776272750
OL,3,CProsecutor 'does not recall knowing
OL,4,CCalocane had students' names in
OL,5,Cweapons bag'
OL,7,F"So I didn't consider that a targeting
OL,8,Fof students provided an appropriate
OL,9,Fexplanation for his conduct that night
OL,10,Fbecause four of his six victims
OL,11,Fplainly were not."
OL,13,FCounsel asked him: "Were you aware in
OL,14,Fthat bag of weapons there was a piece
OL,15,Fof paper with three students names on
OL,16,Fit, three former flatmates names on
OL,17,Fit?"
OL,19,FThe prosecutor said: "I don't now
OL,20,Frecall that, I've become aware of it
OL,21,Fcertainly with time."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@RO]uD@TOUyD@DO]{D@VOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776272750
OL,3,CProsecutor 'does not recall knowing
OL,4,CCalocane had students' names in
OL,5,Cweapons bag'
OL,7,FMs Langdale asked: "Would you like to
OL,8,Fhave been aware of that? With this
OL,9,Fstash of weapons that had been
OL,10,Fprepared and collected on a particular
OL,11,Fbasis, would you like to have seen
OL,12,Fnames on a piece of paper?"
OL,14,FMr Khalil said: "I don't see how it
OL,15,Fwould have affected my decisions in
OL,16,Fthis case."
OL,18,FThis came after the tribunal was shown
OL,19,Fphotographs of two knives and a dagger
OL,20,Fthat Calocane had at the time of the
OL,21,Fattack.
OL,26,@oD@TOUtD@[O]vD@QOUxD@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776272750
OL,3,CProsecutor 'does not recall knowing
OL,4,CCalocane had students' names in
OL,5,Cweapons bag'
OL,7,FMs Langdale also asked the prosecutor
OL,8,Fabout allegations of Calocane fixating
OL,9,Fon and assaulting his former flatmate,
OL,10,Fa student named only as Sebastian.
OL,12,FSebastian previously told the tribunal
OL,13,Fthat Calocane grabbed his shirt and
OL,14,Fpushed him against the wall, and days
OL,15,Flater he heard someone in the flat try
OL,16,Fto open his bedroom door while he was
OL,17,Fsleeping.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776272751
OL,3,CProsecutor 'does not recall knowing
OL,4,CCalocane had students' names in
OL,5,Cweapons bag'
OL,7,FThe inquiry has heard that Calocane
OL,8,Fthen followed Sebastian home on two
OL,9,Foccasions, which he reported to the
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FIn his witness statement, Mr Khalil
OL,13,Fsaid the police's decision to take no
OL,14,Ffurther action on Sebastian's
OL,15,Fallegations was "carefully considered
OL,16,Fand sensible", the tribunal heard.
OL,26,@wD@QOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776272751
OL,3,CProsecutor 'does not recall knowing
OL,4,CCalocane had students' names in
OL,5,Cweapons bag'
OL,7,FMs Langdale put to him: "It speaks for
OL,8,Fitself that you relied on what the
OL,9,Fofficers had recorded at the time to
OL,10,Funderstand those events, and, in
OL,11,Feffect, what may have been the
OL,12,Fcoincidences, and didn't amount to
OL,13,Fvery much from your perspective as the
OL,14,Fprosecutor at this time ` is that a
OL,15,Ffair summary?"
OL,26,@oD@YOUwD@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776272751
OL,3,CProsecutor 'does not recall knowing
OL,4,CCalocane had students' names in
OL,5,Cweapons bag'
OL,7,FMr Khalil replied: "No, it's not that
OL,8,Fit didn't amount to very much, it's
OL,9,Fthat, as described, I didn't see how
OL,10,Fit would alter my judgment as to the
OL,11,Fproper conclusions to reach in this
OL,12,Fcase."
OL,14,FHe was asked if Calocane's assault on
OL,15,FSebastian and his "persistent interest
OL,16,Ftrying to initiate contact with him
OL,17,Fthrough the telephone" would have been
OL,18,Frelevant to his views on Calocane's
OL,19,Fability "to plan and consider" what he
OL,20,Fwas doing.
OL,26,@oD@TOUtD@FO]wD@SOUyD@VO]{D@IOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776272751
OL,3,CProsecutor 'does not recall knowing
OL,4,CCalocane had students' names in
OL,5,Cweapons bag'
OL,7,FMr Khalil said: "When I prepared the
OL,8,Fopening in this case I made it
OL,9,Fabsolutely clear that the Crown's case
OL,10,Fwas that ` although the individuals
OL,11,Fhadn't been pre-selected ` his conduct
OL,12,Fthat night, early morning, involved
OL,13,Fextensive, comprehensive planning."
OL,15,FThis included acquiring weapons,
OL,16,Fchanging clothing and Sim cards and
OL,17,Fhiding in the shadows.
OL,26,@oD@QOUuD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G12/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1776272751
OL,3,CProsecutor 'does not recall knowing
OL,4,CCalocane had students' names in
OL,5,Cweapons bag'
OL,7,F"All of this was indicative of
OL,8,Fplanning and so to find that he has
OL,9,Fhad an obsession with a particular
OL,10,Fperson previously adds to that aspect
OL,11,Fbut it doesn't actually ` in the
OL,12,Fcontext of what he did in this case `
OL,13,Falter any of the decisions that would
OL,14,Fhave flowed from it", Mr Khalil said.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
